  "texts": [
    "Across all model families and sizes, we observe consistent behavioral patterns that align with the aggregated results reported in the main text.",
    "Specifically, Task Arithmetic and its subspace-boosted variant demonstrate robust scaling, maintaining or improving accuracy on diverse benchmarks such as arc_challenge and winogrande as n increases.",
    "In contrast, TIES-Merging, Iso-C and TSV-M suffer from performance degradation on knowledge-intensive and reasoning tasks like medmcqa and mmlu, particularly as the number of merged checkpoints grows.",
    "Model Stock rarely deviates significantly from the base model's performance profile.",
    "These task-level visualizations confirm that the superior average performance of Task Arithmetic is driven by consistent gains across a wide range of evaluation dimensions rather than outliers in specific tasks."
  ],
